<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="17" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1436,257,1074]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,331,941,965]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" reason="1">Etymology.</emphasis>
The name is descriptive for the very long, slender curved spine on the middle of the aedeagal shaft.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
